-- EU's Rehn: Spain must continue reforming pensions
-- 
-- Mon Oct 1, 2012 8:52am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/01/us-spain-economy-pensions-idUSBRE8900M120121001

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - Spain must continue to reform its pensions system, EU Economic and Monetary Affairs Commissioner Olli Rehn said on Monday, adding that the retirement age should rise in line with life expectancy. 
 Rehn was speaking in Madrid after a meeting with Spanish Economy Minister Luis de Guindos. (Reporting By Sarah Morris; Writing by Tracy Rucinski; Editing by Nigel Davies)